{"title":"误会〔外二首〕","authors":["宫?"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":3,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"误会〔外二首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总觉得那楼对我是威胁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庞然，傲然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷冷地对着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴阴地盯着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"操纵黑影压我欺我折磨我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阻挡我的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵吞我的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿嘿地干笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺激我欲哭无泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怪物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这便是时代的骄子么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待到风季雨季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨齐来雷电交加"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地忍无可忍勃然动容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我分明看到那楼悚悚颤栗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它卑微地，谄媚地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向风雨乞怜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向雷电告饶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一扫往日不可一世的威势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仰天大笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知那漫天雷雨中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我几点眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻不容缓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者返回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者就此倒下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者分头四处探察"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者破釜沉舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸黑穿越阴森森的墓地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻不容缓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹豫意味着丧失"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祈祷等于欺骗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侥幸已不可能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无常，随时会乘机袭击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发亮的不全是光明的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明的不全是发亮的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是流萤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是鬼映眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宇宙严守秘密"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切须重新认识"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切须重新开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路已到头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜已深黑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电催逼着快拿主意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失邮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年风雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花还没开你就匆匆离去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仓促间来不及说一声遗憾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此便永无归期"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而Ａ君是摘果之后走的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可他的眼神布满疑虑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他显然感到有些失望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为果子并不如期的甜蜜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们不可能会晤交谈了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使交谈也将话不投机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他会讪笑你那天真的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会斥责他的大胆叛逆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我怎么说呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世事多舛，人生不易"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不知该庆幸的是他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是你"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}